\
\
There is movement in two directions.\
\
Barq and Otto travel counter-clockwise from Borded to Eelan, where they stir up concern that the Wall of Fire could be re-ignited.\
\
Malavorra and Petra (and Kaharan and Allane) travel clockwise from Bordakal to Harvestun. They cross paths on the Ring west of Bordakal. \
